# increase-score

## Feature

Check player or computer score to declare winner

## Acceptance Criteria

### Scenario: Player misses pong ball and computer score increases

  Given game in progress and player misses pong ball

  When computer score increases by 1

  Then check computer score if equal to 11

### Scenario: Computer misses pong ball and player score increases

  Given game in progress and computer misses pong ball

  When player score increases by 1

  Then check player score if equal to 11
